Name: Bulby - Diamond Course
About the game: Help Bulby in this quest to recover the stolen diamonds from the baby princess Natasha! Bulby is a 3D Platformer game which offers either single player or coop Story Mode, and 2 different Versus Mode to play with your friends. You can create your own multiplayer levels and (single or coop) campaign to share on the internet with the built-in Bulby Course Editor.
